rd_id": "Q_447975954", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 345}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "小县城刚上班的女孩子，想买个五菱宏光 mini 做代步，家里人都反对，我该怎么劝说他们？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我离单位不算远，坐公交车有五六站，加上走路和等车的时间，单程要 40 多分钟了，所以想买个代步车，这样就能方便很多。因为刚工作，手头拿不出那么多预算，爸妈答应给出一半，原计划买个五万以内的新车或二手车。选了很久现在我相中了五菱的 mini 做代步，这样我能减轻一些经济压力，还能买个新车，但是爸妈不同意买五菱，他们说你这样还不如买个二手的大品牌车有面子，不过我不这么认为，我觉得我们普通人家开车就是为了方便的，和面子根本没有关系，我该怎么劝说他们呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "502 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/447975954"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImcbJ4qvL45p6EAMaCDYxODI4ODQ4IJmkjoIGMBg4rgZABHIJNDQ3OTc1OTU0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1615172485.1315727", "card_id": "Q_292663930", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 351}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "亲兄弟亲姐妹一个超丑一个超美是什么体验？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-585b7d1eb506ac3c83b3dec9bb959e68_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "433 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/292663930"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImcbJ4qvL45p6EAMaCDI3MzEzMzkyIMGLntwFMAw42QhABXIJMjkyNjYzOTMweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1615172485.1318493", "card_id": "Q_447920058", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 262}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《进击的巨人》漫画最新话，你对艾伦的遭遇有何感受？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "本人艾厨，只有一种果然如此的感觉。我是不是被谏山创刀麻了？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-a8abf2221cc4895d18be1d337e1438c9_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "382 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/447920058"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImcbJ4qvL45p6EAMaCDYxODE2NDE2IOSOjYIGMEA4nwRABnIJNDQ3OTIwMDU4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1615172485.1322153", "card_id": "Q_448089901", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 546}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "代表建议公务员考试打破 35 岁门槛，你有何看法？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "全国人大代表建议公务员考试打破 35 岁门槛 全国人大代表、编剧蒋胜男建议，取消国家公务员报考 35 岁以下的年龄限制。她说，35 岁是一个人做事业最好的黄金年华，也正处在一个艰难的人生阶段，上有老下有小。很多 35 岁以上者在二次就业时遇到年龄歧视。不应该有这种歧视。最重要的是看人的能力和认真工作的态度。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "369 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/448089901"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImcbJ4qvL45p6EAMaCDYxODU0MjI3IOiqkoIGMCw4sQ1AB3IJNDQ4MDg5OTAxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1615172485.1326492", "card_id": "Q_447939211", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1111}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "全国人大代表建议春节假期延长至 10 天，你赞成吗？可行性如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据安徽商报，全国人大代表、肥东县总工会兼职副主席李小莉建议春节假期延长至 10 天，缓解交通压力。李小莉表示，春节期间大量人口集中出行，对交通、旅游资源和公共服务体系形成巨大挑战，超出资源对应的合理人口规模，安全隐患大大增加，交通拥堵让人苦不堪言，安全事故也会增多。若假期延长到 10 天左右的话，既可感受中国传统文化的氛围以及与家人团聚的温暖，也能缓冲一下交通等各方面压力。 全国人大代表：建议春节假期延长至 10 天｜两会聚焦 | 界面新闻 · 快讯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-5df4fd6b354c41c7a9dde73f01922510_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "367 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/447939211"}}, "attached_info": "ClUImcbJ4qvL45p6EAMaCDYxODIwNjU5IPLGjYIGMFQ40BBACHIJNDQ3OTM5MjExeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1615172485.1331801", "card_id": "Q_447858056", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 542}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价腾讯网游加速器在线商城低价出售《鬼谷八荒》的行为?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3f69a36dfe3d310bc705d74aa5319a79_b.jp